### New Files
3. **frontend/src/pages/trading/components/AccountSummaryCard.tsx** (111 行)
   - 账户下拉选择器 (Select, allowClear)
   - Balance / Equity / Margin / FreeMargin / MarginLevel 五列统计卡片
