4. **frontend/src/pages/trading/components/PositionsTable.tsx** (133 行)
   - Ant Design Table: ticket, symbol, side(Tag), volume, openPrice,
     currentPrice, SL, TP, P&L(绿/红色), close 按钮
   - close 按钮使用 Popconfirm 确认弹窗
   - 调用 closeOrder() → 成功后 removePosition() 从 store 移除
