5. **frontend/src/pages/trading/components/PlaceOrderForm.tsx** (96 行)
   - Buy/Sell Radio.Group (buttonStyle="solid")
   - Market/Limit/Stop Radio.Group (buttonStyle="outline")
   - Symbol Input, Volume InputNumber (min=0.01), Price (Limit/Stop 时显示),
     SL InputNumber, TP InputNumber
   - Submit 按钮: loading 绑定 store.loading, disabled 绑定 !accountId,
     danger 绑定 side==='sell'
