   - type 动态推断: market→buy/sell, limit→buy_limit/sell_limit,
     stop→buy_stop/sell_stop

6. **frontend/src/pages/trading/components/OrderHistoryTable.tsx** (101 行)
   - 调用 getOrderHistory({accountId, page, pageSize}) → setOrders/setTotal
   - 分页: Pagination 组件 (showTotal, onChange, pageSize=20)
   - 列: ticket, symbol, type(Tag), volume, openPrice, P&L, openTime
   - useCallback 封装的 loadHistory 避免 effect 无限循环
   - 无 accountId 时清空数据

