   restructured effect to avoid setState-in-setState

## Architecture Notes
- Data flow: tradingStore (Zustand) + useTrading hook + tradingApi client
- All text uses react-i18next useTranslation() with fallback strings
- Components use Ant Design 6 (antd) components: Table, Card, Form,
  InputNumber, Radio, Select, Statistic, Tag, Pagination, Popconfirm
- Type imports: Position from @/types/trading, Account from @/types/account
- All API calls go through useTrading hook (connectRPC-generated client)
- BigInt used for ticket in closeOrder (positions table)

